---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="MVP Development Services - Atiquzzaman Soikat">
  <div class="mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl text-left">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <img src="/logo.svg" alt="Logo" class="w-8 h-8 mx-auto mb-4" />
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">MVP Development Services</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">
        Transform your idea into a working product in weeks, not months
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="mb-6">
        With over 12 years of experience in web development across startups and as a freelancer, I specialize in building 
        Minimum Viable Products (MVPs) that validate your business ideas quickly and efficiently. My approach focuses on 
        delivering clean, maintainable code that prioritizes user experience while meeting your business objectives.
      </p>
      
      <blockquote class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4 mb-8 italic">
        "An MVP is not about building something minimal, but about building the right things that provide maximum value to your users."
      </blockquote>
    </div>

    <!-- Services Grid -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">What I Offer</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
        <!-- Frontend Development -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-600">Frontend Development</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Building responsive, accessible, and performant user interfaces that your customers will love.</p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>React.js
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Next.js
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Svelte
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Vue.js
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>TypeScript
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>TailwindCSS
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Backend Development -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-600">Backend Development</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Creating robust APIs and server-side applications to power your business logic.</p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Node.js
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Express.js
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>PostgreSQL
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>MongoDB
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Firebase
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>REST APIs
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- E-commerce Solutions -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-600">E-commerce Solutions</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Building custom shopping experiences or extending existing platforms to meet your business needs.</p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Shopify
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Custom stores
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Payment integration
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Inventory management
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- JAMstack Websites -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-600">JAMstack Websites</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">Fast, secure, and cost-effective websites built with modern technologies.</p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Astro
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>11ty
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Next.js
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Headless CMS
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mr-2"></span>Strapi
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MVP Process -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">My MVP Development Process</h2>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 h-full w-0.5 bg-gray-200"></div>

        <!-- Process Steps -->
        <div class="relative pl-8 pb-8">
          <div class="absolute left-0 w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full -translate-x-0.5"></div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-lg">1. Discovery & Planning</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">
              We start by understanding your business goals, target users, and core requirements. 
              Together, we'll define what features are essential for your MVP and create a 
              roadmap that aligns with your timeline and budget.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative pl-8 pb-8">
          <div class="absolute left-0 w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full -translate-x-0.5"></div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-lg">2. Design & Architecture</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">
              I'll create a technical architecture that's scalable and maintainable, choosing the right 
              technology stack for your specific needs. We'll focus on designing an intuitive user 
              experience that delivers value from day one.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative pl-8 pb-8">
          <div class="absolute left-0 w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full -translate-x-0.5"></div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-lg">3. Agile Development</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">
              Using an iterative approach, I'll build your MVP in short cycles, allowing for regular 
              feedback and adjustments. This ensures we stay aligned with your vision and can adapt 
              to new insights as they emerge.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative pl-8 pb-8">
          <div class="absolute left-0 w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full -translate-x-0.5"></div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-lg">4. Testing & Quality Assurance</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">
              Every feature is thoroughly tested to ensure reliability, performance, and security. 
              I implement automated testing where appropriate to maintain high quality standards.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative pl-8">
          <div class="absolute left-0 w-2 h-2 bg-blue-500 rounded-full -translate-x-0.5"></div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-lg">5. Launch & Iteration</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">
              We'll deploy your MVP and monitor initial user feedback, making quick iterations to 
              address any issues and improve the product. I'll help you establish metrics to 
              measure success and guide future development decisions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Choose Me -->
    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Why Choose Me For Your MVP</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Experienced Developer</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            12+ years building web applications for startups and enterprises.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Startup Expertise</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Worked with multiple startups like Jetaport, Butler Hospitality, and Skipper Hospitality.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Technical Leadership</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Experience as CTO and Team Lead guiding projects from concept to completion.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Full-Stack Capabilities</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            End-to-end development skills from frontend UIs to backend APIs and databases.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Quality Code</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Clean, maintainable, and well-tested code that can scale as your business grows.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Focus on Business Value</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Building features that align with your core business objectives and user needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="bg-blue-50 p-8 rounded-lg text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Build Your MVP?</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Let's discuss your project and see how I can help bring your idea to life.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-black bg-opacity-80 text-white rounded-md hover:bg-inherit border-1 hover:text-black hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(59,130,246,0.5)] transition-colors transform hover:-translate-y-1 duration-200 shadow-md group">
        <span>Get in Touch</span>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">How long does it take to build an MVP?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Depending on complexity, most MVPs can be built in 4-12 weeks. We'll establish a clear timeline during the discovery phase.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">What's your pricing model?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            I offer both project-based and hourly/monthly retainer options. After understanding your requirements, I'll provide a detailed proposal with transparent pricing.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Do you work remotely?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Yes, I work fully remotely and have experience collaborating with clients and teams worldwide using tools like Slack, Zoom, and Asana.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Who owns the code after the project?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            You do. After completion and final payment, you'll receive full ownership of all code and assets created during the project.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">What happens after the MVP is launched?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            I can continue to support your project with maintenance, bug fixes, and new feature development. We can discuss ongoing support options based on your needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  /* Add any custom styles here */
  .bg-blue-50 {
    background-color: rgba(239, 246, 255, 0.6);
  }
</style>